Ford China Sales Rise 3% in July to 32,320 Vehicles

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-08-11T00:55:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-11/ford-china-sales-rise-3-in-july-to-32-320-vehicles.html
Ford Motor Co. said its China sales
rose 3 percent in July from a year earlier to 32,320 vehicles,
according to an e-mailed statement from the company today.  Sales in the first seven months gained 13 percent to
306,830 units, the statement said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Chua Kong Ho in Shanghai at 
